<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/electricity-settlements-company> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "ESC is responsible for financial transactions relating to the energy Capacity Market, including making capacity payments to capacity providers, controlling collateral and managing auction bid bonds. ESC works with the Department for Energy Security and Net Zero ."@en .
